{
    "publish_date": "2012-11-27T19:56:46.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT14M35S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: This week I&#39;m\nhere with Miguel Galluzzi,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": "0"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycle designer\nextraordinaire.", 
            "dur": "0.856", 
            "start": "0"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we&#39;re going to\ntalk bikes past,", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "0.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "present, and also future.", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "3.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Welcome to RideApart.", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "4.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "36.703", 
            "start": "6.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Oh,\nI&#39;m excited today.", 
            "dur": "1.104", 
            "start": "43.199"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re here to see\nMiguel Galluzzi.", 
            "dur": "2.283", 
            "start": "44.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now this gentleman, he&#39;s\nresponsible for designing the", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "46.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ducati Monster, the Aprilia\nDorsoduro, the Aprilia RSV4.", 
            "dur": "4.83", 
            "start": "49.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now he&#39;s with Moto Guzzi.", 
            "dur": "1.11", 
            "start": "54.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Jamie.", 
            "dur": "0.922", 
            "start": "55.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: How are you?", 
            "dur": "0.898", 
            "start": "56.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: How are you?", 
            "dur": "0.81", 
            "start": "57.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Fantastic,\nyou?", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "58.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Yeah.", 
            "dur": "0.44", 
            "start": "59.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Wonderful.", 
            "dur": "0.35", 
            "start": "59.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Nice\nto see you.", 
            "dur": "1.189", 
            "start": "60.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: And you.", 
            "dur": "0.491", 
            "start": "61.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;ve all got beautiful\nmotorcycles here.", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "61.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Read to ride.", 
            "dur": "0.91", 
            "start": "64.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Ready\nto ride, eh?", 
            "dur": "1.83", 
            "start": "65.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All motorcycles should\nbe ready to ride.", 
            "dur": "1.77", 
            "start": "66.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Absolutely.", 
            "dur": "1.416", 
            "start": "68.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: So your love\nfor motorcycles goes back", 
            "dur": "1.724", 
            "start": "70.162"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quite a long way?", 
            "dur": "0.8", 
            "start": "71.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI:\nOh, in my case?", 
            "dur": "0.79", 
            "start": "72.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, yeah.", 
            "dur": "0.57", 
            "start": "73.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A long, long way.", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "74.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think I was eight and my\nbrother and I, we are a year", 
            "dur": "7.67", 
            "start": "76.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "apart, so he was born the\n25th of October and I", 
            "dur": "4.31", 
            "start": "84.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was born the 26th.", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "88.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am older, so there is one day\nthat we are the same age.", 
            "dur": "3.42", 
            "start": "90.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the birthday parties\nwere the same day.", 
            "dur": "4.25", 
            "start": "93.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was hoping to\nget a drum set.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "98.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I wanted to\nbe a drummer.", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "101.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Instead my uncle gave\nus a motorcycle, a", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "104.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "50cc something there.", 
            "dur": "4.38", 
            "start": "106.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we were really\ndisappointed.", 
            "dur": "1.42", 
            "start": "111.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because we really\nwanted drums.", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "112.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And from that moment on,\nwe never stopped.", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "115.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My brother still races\nbikes in Argentina.", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "118.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m been involved with\nbikes since then.", 
            "dur": "4.599", 
            "start": "121.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We grew up racing in the &#39;70s.", 
            "dur": "2.226", 
            "start": "126.495"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know, Motocross was\nthe big thing in &#39;72,", 
            "dur": "3.655", 
            "start": "128.721"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&#39;73, &#39;74, until &#39;78.", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "132.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then from that moment\non I wanted to", 
            "dur": "4.71", 
            "start": "135.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "design things, to invent.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "140.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I just finished the military\nservice in", 
            "dur": "2.01", 
            "start": "142.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Argentina in the &#39;70s.", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "144.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it was doing the\ndesaparacidos story there.", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "147.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I was 18, 19, and I said, I\nam going to leave this country", 
            "dur": "4.02", 
            "start": "150.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s a mess.", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "154.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I went to Florida to study\nmechanical engineering there.", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "156.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then discovered\nArt Center.", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "160.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I started reading English and\nstarted understanding a little", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "162.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bit more what&#39;s the\nworld about.", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "165.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I discovered this school\nand then transferred.", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "168.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s it.", 
            "dur": "1.346", 
            "start": "172.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: What\na journey.", 
            "dur": "0.614", 
            "start": "174.322"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So your first experience with\nmotorcycles really must have", 
            "dur": "4.13", 
            "start": "174.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "touched you deep.", 
            "dur": "1.1", 
            "start": "179.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because from there, of not\nknowing anything about", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "180.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycles, it became\npart of your entire--", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "182.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: No.", 
            "dur": "0.26", 
            "start": "184.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The problem--", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "185.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it was a problem--", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "186.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the day I was born, my father\nwas racing a motorcycle--", 
            "dur": "4.8", 
            "start": "190.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "four days after, as\nI discovered on my", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "195.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "last trip to Argentina.", 
            "dur": "1.08", 
            "start": "199.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For days after I was born he\nwon a big motorcycle race.", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "200.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then with that money he could\ntake me out of the hospital.", 
            "dur": "3.152", 
            "start": "204.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this was on November 1,\n1959, he won the race.", 
            "dur": "5.878", 
            "start": "207.218"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was born in a family that\nmy grandfather used to", 
            "dur": "6.65", 
            "start": "213.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "race motorcycles.", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "219.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Harley Davidsons\nin 1916, 1920s.", 
            "dur": "4.94", 
            "start": "222.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have some pictures\nsomeplace.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "227.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But then my father started\nbicycling and then", 
            "dur": "3.14", 
            "start": "228.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycling and then racing.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "232.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I was born in this family So\neven though I wanted to be", 
            "dur": "4.58", 
            "start": "234.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a drummer, a musician, I ended\nup doing what I was not", 
            "dur": "4.2", 
            "start": "238.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "planning to do.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "242.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The funny part was, my uncles\nand father raced road racing.", 
            "dur": "5.76", 
            "start": "245.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The new thing in the\n&#39;70s was Motocross.", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "250.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So there was a cultural clash.", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "253.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because they will be road racers\nand leather and things.", 
            "dur": "3.92", 
            "start": "256.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we will be Motocross,\ndirt and whatever.", 
            "dur": "4.86", 
            "start": "260.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that was the only part that\nwe were separated from what", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "265.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they&#39;d been doing for\nquite a long time.", 
            "dur": "1.83", 
            "start": "268.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Dirt biking,\nyou&#39;re always", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "270.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "having fun dirk biking.", 
            "dur": "1.06", 
            "start": "272.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not quite the\nsame, is it?", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "273.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Oh.", 
            "dur": "0.69", 
            "start": "274.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The good part about Motocross at\nthat time-- and I think it", 
            "dur": "4.17", 
            "start": "275.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "still is like that--", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "279.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is when you gather\nwith some friends", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "281.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then you go riding.", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "283.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In our case, we would go to\nthese areas that you can ride.", 
            "dur": "5.5", 
            "start": "285.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There was not actually\na track.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "290.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But we would just ride, maybe a\nwhole Sunday from morning to", 
            "dur": "4.56", 
            "start": "292.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "night, until you couldn&#39;t\nbreathe anymore.", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "297.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it was the fun part of going\nand jumping and killing", 
            "dur": "3.78", 
            "start": "299.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "yourself, too.", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "303.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you would go\ndown or whatever.", 
            "dur": "1.59", 
            "start": "304.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Whatever it is, it was\nthe fun part of it.", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "305.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: And that&#39;s where\nyou learn skills, as", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "308.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "well, on the dirt.", 
            "dur": "0.74", 
            "start": "309.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And learn how to ride.", 
            "dur": "1.165", 
            "start": "310.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it makes it easier\nfor the road.", 
            "dur": "1.725", 
            "start": "311.371"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Yeah.", 
            "dur": "0.14", 
            "start": "313.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Especially, especially when\nyou are falling down.", 
            "dur": "5.48", 
            "start": "313.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You start understanding that you\ncan do something and not", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "318.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hit the ground.", 
            "dur": "0.85", 
            "start": "321.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: What is\nthe message that&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "322.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "being presented now?", 
            "dur": "1.09", 
            "start": "323.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because like you said, it seems\nlike all of the fun is", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "324.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "being taken out of\nmotorcycling.", 
            "dur": "1.42", 
            "start": "327.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And motorcycling is one of the\nmost fun things we can do on", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "328.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the planet.", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "331.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the message is--?", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "332.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: But that&#39;s part\nof what we have lost in", 
            "dur": "1.98", 
            "start": "335.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the last 10 years,\nmaybe, or 15.", 
            "dur": "4.64", 
            "start": "337.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What I say, is we became too\nintelligent for our own sake.", 
            "dur": "4.58", 
            "start": "342.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We are so smart that we are\ndoing the wrong stuff.", 
            "dur": "3.55", 
            "start": "346.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Especially motorcycling, as I\nsaid, look at an advertisement", 
            "dur": "8.01", 
            "start": "350.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "today and it doesn&#39;t\nmake sense.", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "358.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even the cover of Cycle World\nthis month, as I was telling", 
            "dur": "3.54", 
            "start": "361.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you before, if you see the\namount of plastic that", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "365.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycle has, plastic means\nthere are some pieces that are", 
            "dur": "4.93", 
            "start": "368.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "covering something else.", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "373.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the end, do we\nneed all that?", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "375.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No.", 
            "dur": "0.69", 
            "start": "377.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because if you want to commute,\nwe can get a scooter", 
            "dur": "4.09", 
            "start": "378.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "3.05", 
            "start": "382.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If we have to ride, maybe\ntravel, where are", 
            "dur": "4.17", 
            "start": "385.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re going to go?", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "389.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe you need another\ntype of bike.", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "391.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Are you going to go enjoy the\nride, just for the sake of it?", 
            "dur": "3.91", 
            "start": "393.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You don&#39;t need all that stuff.", 
            "dur": "1.155", 
            "start": "397.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: So how have we\ngone from the enjoyment of", 
            "dur": "3.285", 
            "start": "398.731"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycling, which we saw there\nback in the &#39;50s and", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "402.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&#39;60s and even into the &#39;70s,\nto where we are now with", 
            "dur": "3.17", 
            "start": "404.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "plastic-looking motorcycles that\nlook like they can all do", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "408.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "200 miles an hour?", 
            "dur": "3.55", 
            "start": "410.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: How\ndid we get there?", 
            "dur": "0.62", 
            "start": "414.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: How\ndid we get there?", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "414.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Not\nunderstanding what", 
            "dur": "0.95", 
            "start": "417.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycling all about.", 
            "dur": "1.775", 
            "start": "418.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: And what,\nin your opinion, is", 
            "dur": "1.615", 
            "start": "420.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycling all about?", 
            "dur": "1.12", 
            "start": "421.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: It&#39;s\nto enjoy the ride.", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "422.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That is the simplest, most idiot\nthing to think about.", 
            "dur": "6.5", 
            "start": "424.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In any condition, because you\ncan go riding in the desert,", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "431.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can go riding in the\nmountains, you can go riding", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "434.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the city.", 
            "dur": "1.09", 
            "start": "436.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can even commute.", 
            "dur": "1.74", 
            "start": "437.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when you commute and you\nunderstand that the streets", 
            "dur": "3.14", 
            "start": "439.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are not full of cars and there\nis a lot of space that is not", 
            "dur": "4.42", 
            "start": "442.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "being used, then you understand\nthat it&#39;s more fun", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "447.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to commute when you\nhave two wheels.", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "449.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Are you\ntrying to get that", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "453.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "across in your designs?", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "454.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Bringing back the fun\nelement, and the--", 
            "dur": "5.44", 
            "start": "456.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: To me, as I\nalways said, in my profession", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "461.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as a designer I always\ntry to be simple", 
            "dur": "3.68", 
            "start": "465.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "designs that are strong.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "468.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because like we were saying with\nsome friends, there is", 
            "dur": "3.73", 
            "start": "471.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "design and there is\ndesign with soul.", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "475.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Soul lasts forever.", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "477.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This friend of mine yesterday\nnight got some pictures of", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "479.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Figoni et Falaschi cars\nfrom the &#39;30s.", 
            "dur": "3.82", 
            "start": "483.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there are things that you\nsee today and your breath is", 
            "dur": "5.96", 
            "start": "487.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "taken away by something that\nis 80, 100 years old.", 
            "dur": "4.14", 
            "start": "493.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that is good design, because\nit lasts forever.", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "497.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What we were saying about the\nplastic part of today&#39;s bikes.", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "501.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Plastic is taking the\neasy way out.", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "504.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So in the end, these pieces\nof plastic right now--", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "508.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this is something we\ndiscovered with the Guzzi--", 
            "dur": "3.929", 
            "start": "511.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the side panel there is\naluminum, it costs less than", 
            "dur": "4.171", 
            "start": "515.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the same part painted\nin plastic.", 
            "dur": "4.15", 
            "start": "519.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: But you see,\nplastic on motorcycles, for", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "523.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "me, only really belonged\non dirt bikes.", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "526.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I grew up with the\ninfluence of a father who had", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "529.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "British motorcycles in his\ngarage, a BSA Gold Star and", 
            "dur": "3.56", 
            "start": "532.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that kind of motorcycle.", 
            "dur": "1.26", 
            "start": "536.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I grew up seeing a\nmotorcycle that was beautiful", 
            "dur": "3.61", 
            "start": "537.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in design, very simple\nin design as well.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "540.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But everything on there\nhad a purpose.", 
            "dur": "3.33", 
            "start": "543.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: I always\nremember the guys who used to", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "547.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "design Nortons in the\n&#39;40s and &#39;50s.", 
            "dur": "3.55", 
            "start": "549.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I read [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "1.02", 
            "start": "552.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "history that their minds--", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "553.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and these were craftsmen, they\nwere not designers and", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "556.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "engineers, they were people\nthat were really", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "559.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there with the tape--", 
            "dur": "1.92", 
            "start": "561.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "each piece has to be fast.", 
            "dur": "1.69", 
            "start": "563.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s what I remember\nthey were thinking.", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "564.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And every part that they would\ndo has to be fast.", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "566.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: I don&#39;t\nknow how you feel,", 
            "dur": "0.85", 
            "start": "569.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but your wife rides.", 
            "dur": "1.36", 
            "start": "569.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there isn&#39;t that many bikes\nthat appeal to women,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "571.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "either, are there?", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "573.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: For example,\none good story, success story", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "575.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about the Monster for Ducati\nthere was a lot of women got", 
            "dur": "5.7", 
            "start": "578.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into motorcycling\nbecause of that.", 
            "dur": "1.985", 
            "start": "584.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And not because it was the\nfastest or whatever.", 
            "dur": "3.175", 
            "start": "586.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The 600 Monster was great,\nbecause as I said before, they", 
            "dur": "3.78", 
            "start": "589.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "could get into the bike and\ntheir two feet were flat on", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "593.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the ground.", 
            "dur": "1.01", 
            "start": "595.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that makes a sensation\nof yeah, I can do this.", 
            "dur": "3.575", 
            "start": "596.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: And how is it\nworking with the Italians?", 
            "dur": "1.805", 
            "start": "599.791"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because they&#39;re very passionate\npeople and you&#39;ve", 
            "dur": "1.88", 
            "start": "601.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "designed some incredible\nmotorcycles for them.", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "603.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: My experience,\nfor example, in 18", 
            "dur": "4.28", 
            "start": "606.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "years in Cagiva we have\ndone maybe 400 bikes.", 
            "dur": "5.73", 
            "start": "610.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe five went in production.", 
            "dur": "2.27", 
            "start": "616.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But just to keep the mind\nworking ahead and trying", 
            "dur": "5.37", 
            "start": "618.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "things that maybe\nyou throw away.", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "623.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But not spending\na lot of money.", 
            "dur": "1.48", 
            "start": "626.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s the point.", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "627.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe we&#39;ll do a new form\nand do something", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "628.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you throw away.", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "630.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then you go to\nsomething else.", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "632.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That gives you windows\nthat you open.", 
            "dur": "3.9", 
            "start": "634.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, we&#39;re going to see this.", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "638.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, no, this doesn&#39;t work,\nwe&#39;re going to do that.", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "639.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then you keep on trying\nuntil you find", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "642.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "something that is right.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "644.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: That&#39;s\nevolution also.", 
            "dur": "0.58", 
            "start": "645.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everything is moving forwards.", 
            "dur": "1.19", 
            "start": "646.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: But it\nworks from the gut.", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "647.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It doesn&#39;t work from\nspecific planning.", 
            "dur": "5.09", 
            "start": "649.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Specific planning\nworks sometimes.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "654.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it&#39;s more related to\nproducts of big production.", 
            "dur": "5", 
            "start": "656.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: And were you\nreally trying to get a Cafe", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "661.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Racer look from this or did it\njust evolve that way when you", 
            "dur": "3.292", 
            "start": "663.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "were putting pen to paper?", 
            "dur": "2.188", 
            "start": "666.548"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: In Guzzi,\nthe V7 Sport from", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "668.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the &#39;70s, is an icon.", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "671.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this didn&#39;t want to be like\nthat because that was a", 
            "dur": "4.12", 
            "start": "674.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "big bike, big super\nbike at that time.", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "678.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even though it was the\nsame size as this.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "681.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s what, to me, Guzzi\nrepresented in", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "685.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these kind of bikes.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "688.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Like [INAUDIBLE],\nthe [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "689.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was really an evolution\nof the V7.", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "691.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that was a very simple\nand it gets you.", 
            "dur": "5.31", 
            "start": "693.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you see it today, even\ntoday, it gets you.", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "698.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Whoa, that&#39;s a nice bike.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "700.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So trying to get that\ninspiration in this motorcycle", 
            "dur": "4.64", 
            "start": "702.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was one of our considerations.", 
            "dur": "1.94", 
            "start": "707.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: So what\nabout the future?", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "709.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What about motorcycles in\nthe future and were", 
            "dur": "1.623", 
            "start": "711.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are we going to go?", 
            "dur": "0.667", 
            "start": "713.519"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: The\nfuture is bright.", 
            "dur": "1.745", 
            "start": "714.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s go over there.", 
            "dur": "1.925", 
            "start": "715.931"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, that&#39;s the fun\npart, as I said.", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "717.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because we are thinking\neverything, all different", 
            "dur": "4.48", 
            "start": "720.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "parts of what the\nfuture could be.", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "724.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to me, it goes through the\nsimple stuff that you can", 
            "dur": "3.57", 
            "start": "727.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "enjoy the ride.", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "731.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It could even be electric,\nwith an", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "733.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "electric batter or whatever.", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "735.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: When I ride the\nmotorcycle, an electric", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "737.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "motorcycle, I am actually\ntotally enjoying the entire", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "738.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "experience.", 
            "dur": "0.79", 
            "start": "741.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I&#39;m still riding a\nmotorcycle, I have handlebars,", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "741.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am in control.", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "743.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It does what I want it to do.", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "744.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there&#39;s something missing.", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "747.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: The noise\nis another type of noise.", 
            "dur": "4.44", 
            "start": "749.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which is not the noise I like.", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "753.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Not\nfor me, I feel--", 
            "dur": "0.66", 
            "start": "756.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Or you like.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "756.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that&#39;s the change, the\nbig generational change.", 
            "dur": "5.35", 
            "start": "758.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, these 20-something\npeople have grown up with the", 
            "dur": "4.98", 
            "start": "764.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "PlayStation, with\na noise which is", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "769.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not the regular noise.", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "770.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It doesn&#39;t make it\nbetter, or--", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "772.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just like that.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "774.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re going to still\nenjoy the ride.", 
            "dur": "4.13", 
            "start": "775.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re going to still be able to\nride without going into the", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "779.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "gas station.", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "782.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And having your bike or whatever\nit is that you&#39;re", 
            "dur": "2.85", 
            "start": "784.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "going to have in a\ndifferent way.", 
            "dur": "2.952", 
            "start": "787.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Fancy\ngoing for a ride?", 
            "dur": "1.85", 
            "start": "790.218"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Yeah, why not?", 
            "dur": "0.948", 
            "start": "792.068"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s go.", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "793.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "47.18", 
            "start": "794.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Wow, what\na fascinating day.", 
            "dur": "1.985", 
            "start": "841.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hasn&#39;t it been incredible going\ninto this man&#39;s mind?", 
            "dur": "2.677", 
            "start": "843.611"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s been a pleasure.", 
            "dur": "1.548", 
            "start": "846.288"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI:\nOh, thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.4", 
            "start": "847.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you for coming.", 
            "dur": "0.66", 
            "start": "849.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Yeah.", 
            "dur": "0.49", 
            "start": "849.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s been absolutely brilliant\nlistening to you and really", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "850.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "getting the whole concept of\nyour design and what you feel", 
            "dur": "3.33", 
            "start": "853.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about motorcycles.", 
            "dur": "0.9", 
            "start": "856.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Let&#39;s\ndo it again.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "857.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: Absolutely.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "859.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thanks again.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "860.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MIGUEL GALLUZZI: Thank\nyou, Jamie.", 
            "dur": "0.59", 
            "start": "860.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All the best.", 
            "dur": "0.8", 
            "start": "861.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "JAMIE ROBINSON: And thank\nyou for the espresso.", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "862.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "8.315", 
            "start": "863.556"
        }
